modName: Upgrade and fix for TreesHD  by Pfuscher
summary: This mod fixes the seam and has twice the performance with the exact same visual quality.
descriptionHtml:
This mod fixes the seam (treepineforestbarkcomp3) and has twice the performance with the exact same visual quality. (Ultra version 1k x 4k trees)
Just overwrite your files with this.
All props and Credits to namotep, just wanted to increase performance and fix that seam. It's now again compatible with SFO 2.0
Original mod
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3812/?

If you want 2k, use texture optimizer

Don't ask for the branches I've changed in that picture. That's Vurt's stuff, I just changed it to my personal preferation.
